{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-3","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">AM</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">PM</span> se koriste za prikaz vremena dana. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">AM</span> znači period od ponoći do dana (na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">8:00 AM</span> je jutro). <span class=\"highlighted-text\">PM</span> znači period od dana do ponoći (na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">6:00 PM</span> je večer).</p>\n<p>Na engleskom jeziku, dan je podeljen na dva perioda koristeći <span class=\"highlighted-text\">AM</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">PM</span>. <span class=\"highlighted-text\">AM</span> znači za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Ante Meridiem</span>, što je latinski izraz za \"pre podne\". Odnosi se na vreme od ponoći (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">12:00 AM</span>) do podne (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">12:00 PM</span>). Dakle, kada kažete <span class=\"highlighted-text\">9:00 AM</span>, to znači devet sati ujutru.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">PM</span> znači <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Post Meridiem</span>, što je latinski za \"nakon popodne\". Odnosi se na period od dana (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">12:00 PM</span>) do skoro ponoći (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">11:59 PM</span>). Dakle, kada kažete <span class=\"highlighted-text\">3:00 PM</span>, to znači 3 sata popodne.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-3"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koja fraza je tačna?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">10:00 AM</span> je sredina noći.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">10:00 AM</span> To je jutro, nije ponoć.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">12:00 PM</span> To je dan.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">7:00 PM</span> To je vrlo rano ujutro.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">7:00 PM</span> Veče je, nije vrlo jutro.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">1:00 AM</span> je dečak.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">1:00 AM</span> to je rano ujutro, nije dan.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 3","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","dashedName":"task-3","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-4","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-2","id":"657e05f30925c93d93c03fe3","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-3"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}